2.4.11-1 (2013-01-01)
    - call sophomorix-bind on samba login working
    - More loggin enabled:
      sophomorix-bind logs to:
         /tmp/sophomorix-bind.login 
         /tmp/sophomorix-bind.logout
      Calling sophomorix-bind is called in: 
         /var/lib/sophomorix/command.log

